Everybody in the Big Boom Motel is being hold hostage by the terrorist! 
The Counter Terrorist are trying there best to get the hosties out of the building. 

After the t's been bombing the motel the cts have been keeping a close eye on them.
Suprised its still in buisness after all the t's have done.

They are demanding that the ct's give them an awp and they will let the hostages go!
